29 if (nbytes <= sizeof(elfhdr))
30 return 0;
31
32 u.l = 1;
33 (void)memcpy(&elfhdr, buf, sizeof elfhdr);
34 swap = (u.c[sizeof(int32_t) - 1] + 1) != elfhdr.e_ident[EI_DATA];
35
36 type = elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_type);
37 notecount = ms->elf_notes_max;
38 switch (type) {
39#ifdef ELFCORE
40 case ET_CORE:
41 phnum = elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_phnum);
42 if (phnum > ms->elf_phnum_max)
43 return toomany(ms, "program headers", phnum);
44 flags |= FLAGS_IS_CORE;
45 if (dophn_core(ms, clazz, swap, fd,
46 CAST(off_t, elf_getu(swap, elfhdr.e_phoff)), phnum,
47 CAST(size_t, elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_phentsize)),
48 fsize, &flags, &notecount) == -1)
49 return -1;
50 break;
51#endif
52 case ET_EXEC:
53 case ET_DYN:
54 phnum = elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_phnum);
55 if (phnum > ms->elf_phnum_max)
56 return toomany(ms, "program", phnum);
57 shnum = elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_shnum);
58 if (shnum > ms->elf_shnum_max)
59 return toomany(ms, "section", shnum);
60 if (dophn_exec(ms, clazz, swap, fd,
61 CAST(off_t, elf_getu(swap, elfhdr.e_phoff)), phnum,
62 CAST(size_t, elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_phentsize)),
63 fsize, shnum, &flags, &notecount) == -1)
64 return -1;
65 /*FALLTHROUGH*/
66 case ET_REL:
67 shnum = elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_shnum);
68 if (shnum > ms->elf_shnum_max)
69 return toomany(ms, "section headers", shnum);
70 if (doshn(ms, clazz, swap, fd,
71 CAST(off_t, elf_getu(swap, elfhdr.e_shoff)), shnum,
72 CAST(size_t, elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_shentsize)),
73 fsize, elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_machine),
74 CAST(int, elf_getu16(swap, elfhdr.e_shstrndx)),
75 &flags, &notecount) == -1)
76 return -1;
77 break;
78
79 default:
80 break;
81 }
82 if (notecount == 0)
83 return toomany(ms, "notes", ms->elf_notes_max);
84 return 1;
